.landing-container
  .landing-console
    .landing-graybox
      .landing-logo
        %img{:src => "http://i.imgur.com/tTRdWNT.gif"}/
    / -the div below is hidden
    = form_for(resource, as: resource_name, url: registration_path(resource_name)) do |f|
      .landing-interior_two
        = devise_error_messages!
        = f.email_field :email, autofocus: true, class: "sign_in landing", placeholder: "Email"
        = f.password_field :password, autocomplete: "off", class: "sign_in landing", placeholder: "Password"
        = f.password_field :password_confirmation, autocomplete: "off", class: "sign_in landing", placeholder: "Confirm Password"
        %ul.landing-buttons
          %li.landing-login.landing
            %a= f.submit "Sign Up", class: "landing-noUnderline landing"
    / links or forgot password
    .landing-forgot_password
      %a.landing-noUnderline.landing{:href => "#"} Forgot Password?
  .landing-right
    %h2.landing Sending files. Simplified.
    %p.landing
      File exchange should be a hassle-free part of your business. With T.BOX, files are sent and retrieved via unique URLs. Just log-in, select a box, and upload. Your customers don't need to set up an account to be able to upload into your box. To access your files, all they need is the box's unique URL. Quick and easy.
      %a.landing-noUnderline_white{:href => "#"} Click here to find out more.
